reviewText: Theis DVD has been more of a challenge for me to play.  We  have a location 1 and 2  world player but sometimes this DVD gets stuck in the party mode and ask us to use a computer to clear the Cd Rom drive.  But we have found that if we keep using the menu on the played eventually we get to the story.
I received a DVDs that does not work in the United States. I have asked how to return it and have not received any information...
